# bundle_a.show — HIL L3 fixture: 2 fixtures, 0 matrices.
#
# Compiled by conftest.py's compile_show_bundle() (the `provision` host
# tool) and flashed straight to the "show" raw partition. Paired with
# bundle_b.show so L3 can assert "swap bundles -> counts change" against
# two known-different bundles instead of a single static one.
#
# Run from the repo root so samples/dimmer.fdef resolves (see
# samples/demo.show's own comment on this).

UNIVERSE 0 DMX

FIXTURE samples/dimmer.fdef 0 0
FIXTURE samples/dimmer.fdef 0 10
